#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/hell_hound.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Armor Class** 15 (natural armor)    \n"
"**Hit Points** 45 (7d8 + 14)    \n"
"**Speed** 50 ft. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/hell_hound.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| STR     | DEX     | CON     | INT     | WIS     | CHA     |\n"
"|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|\n"
"| 17 (+3) | 12 (+1) | 14 (+2) | 6 (−2)  | 13 (+1) | 6 (−2)  |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/hell_hound.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Skills** Perception +5    \n"
"**Damage Immunities** fire    \n"
"**Senses** darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 15    \n"
"**Languages** understands Infernal but can't speak it    \n"
"**Challenge** 3 (700 XP) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/hell_hound.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Keen Hearing and Smell.** The hound has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) "
"checks that rely on hearing or smell.    \n"
"**Pack Tactics.** The hound has advantage on an attack roll against a "
"creature if at least one of the hound's allies is within 5 feet of the "
"creature and the ally isn't incapacitated. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/hell_hound.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions    \n"
"**Bite.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"7 (1d8 + 3) piercing damage plus 7 (2d6) fire damage.    \n"
"**Fire Breath (Recharge 5–6).** The hound exhales fire in a 15-foot "
"cone. Each creature in that area must make a DC 12 Dexterity saving throw, "
"taking 21 (6d6) fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a "
"successful one.\n"
msgstr ""
